      <odd id="aspace_f4645457fe81b685015c9d2f48cd6c99">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-A (YRG 46-A), Records and materials broadly documenting Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <prefercite id="aspace_ed7305d90e8865c8c2d60f4badc5068f">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Loveday Yates Sketches of Yale University (RU 640). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_1be09909a94f322adb41d403a6d0cfcc">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <arrangement id="aspace_aec14a4a02baa01a703943efa9018099">
